u heard about our marital problems. Every platform dies the same way, and you may have noticed right now that Imgur is likely deep in its own collapse. I sat down with my longtime friend TylerFromTheInternet to talk about “Ensh*ttification” - how apps hook us, bleed us, and then betray us.

https://youtu.be/jfWcoJxo7C8

Want to know what has been going on here the past couple months?

In the full video, we break down what’s happening to Imgur right now (13:27), the mass staff firings from MediaLabs (19:17), when Imgur literally broke (21:24), and how banning, blackouts, and even “The Boob Phase” (30:25) fit into the bigger picture. Along the way we hit Fark, iMDB, Reddit’s failures, and even why Mitt Romney somehow hates Tyler.

It’s funny, furious, and maybe a little depressing - but if you’ve ever loved this site, you’ll want to see how it all fits together.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/j8xtMJ7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Alsoashley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What do we have here?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VXN7uU1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xh7FQPO.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VXN7uU1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DOcelot1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Joyride</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kJH4spi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rEtXIuJ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#awesome #funny #dog #cute #mildly_interesting</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/kJH4spi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[OceansRust]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Well that be something</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/rkDIkvQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x03E0MU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/rkDIkvQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LordoftheHildago]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Box turtles are aptly named as they can completely close up their shell like a box</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KjmjTmH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L4rwOCy.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KjmjTmH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vefivos]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Free speech now has a cost…</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/dGVd9Ac</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1ahpXou.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div