ax-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>These are genocidal thugs, all of them are white supremacists who committed/encouraged violence against minorities and the left, the world would be better off if all of them were dead. You should have less than zero sympathy for barely human scum like this.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zEIa3HO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Freyja33]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/bxngKaQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cLIXYKx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/bxngKaQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[trinxter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Return of the Meme: 1476 (bleak meme)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nOaS2O4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h7P4foK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Let's get this bread.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TQnjeEO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A friend of mine who's a teacher is getting doxxed, fired, and banned from working in her town by the schoolboard courtesy of posting a "celebratory" Kirk meme. She is considering moving to another state.  Welcome to rural MAGA Arizona.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EOceV3c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Also, someone stole my laundry basket at the apartment laundry room.  I had to carry all my laundry back to my apartment by hand.

