EDIT #2: After an emergency vet visit today, it looks like Luna has lost a lot of weight. The vet is very concerned. We're hoping it's something viral and she has been prescribed an antibiotic. But the reality is that she is a very old girl and we may just be providing her with end of life care. She may have a cancer or something else that we're not able to see externally. Besides her weight loss, she's got a little bit of a fever and we're hoping that whatever is bothering her is a minor infection. However, like I told the doctor, so long as she keeps showing me that will to go on, I will do everything I can for her. She's my baby.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/mTVk66u</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheUnnamedPoet]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Oh Yeah...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ZiRZ3ns</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oLYAttG.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I was a firefighter almsot 40 years ago (fuck me...) but I can attest, yes, this is true. If you were dumb enough to park in front of a hydrant all of us are eager to bust out your windows to run hose.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ZiRZ3ns</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MightyUrto]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What happened at Delta State University?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7BLD0X5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IQpUzo4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://m.economictimes.com/news/international/global-trends/us-news-trey-reeds-death-sparks-outrage-black-people-dont-lynch-themselves-says-internet-after-delta-state-university-statement/articleshow/123925352.cms</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/7BLD0X5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dragoncloud9]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>We call them Crowd Earmuffs in my family</title><link>https://imgur.com/g